Where is this picture from? How do I use Reverse Image Search to find the source of an anime/manga image? So I see an image from what I believe is from either an anime or manga. What are some ways that I can go about finding what series it's from?
Try these options:

Google reverse image search (browser built-in support and plugins)
Other reverse image search engines: TinEye, SauceNao, iqdb
Technique: Cropping the image
Animated GIF: Picking the right frame


Note: If you followed these methods and could not identify your image, you're welcome to ask a question tagged identification-request. Be sure to mention that you followed these steps and what results (if any) you saw. Reading these guidelines can prevent getting your question closed for lack of details.



Protip: If you are using Google Image Search in a non-English language, change your language to English for better, more accurate results.
